Package org.apache.wayang.core.mathex

Interface MathExListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
MathExBaseListener
public interface MathExListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by MathExParser.
